rm that could help it continue growing rapidly in the coming years. While the stock has reached</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2096475191/image_2096475191.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743576-zeta-global-value-play-post-omnicom-interpublic-merger", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 18:00:57"}, {"id": "4743571", "title": "AMD Is Back In The Buy Zone (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AMD headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1679336666\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>In light of its <a href=\"https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_9dbb409594957336af50b3d0d14cd8bd/amd/news/2024-10-29_AMD_Reports_Third_Quarter_2024_Financial_1224.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Q3 2024 report</a>, I downgraded semiconductor giant <b>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a></span>) stock to a \"Hold\" rating, citing its inadequate long-term risk/reward:</p> <blockquote> <p><em>In Q3, AMD beat consensus estimates but failed to deliver superlative guidance. As I</em></p> </blockquote>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679336666/image_1679336666.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743571-amd-is-back-in-the-buy-zone-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 17:53:39"}, {"id": "4743588", "title": "Communications Services Leads U.S. Equity Sectors In 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesswoman checking app on smart phone while working on web design in studio\" data-id=\"1139932722\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1139932722/image_1139932722.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/11399327